  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "商君者，衛之諸庶孽公子也，名鞅，姓公孫氏，其祖本姬姓也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "鞅少好刑名之學，事魏相公叔座為中庶子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "公叔座知其賢，未及進。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "會座病，魏惠王親往問病，曰：「公叔病有如不可諱，將柰社稷何？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "」公叔曰：「座之中庶子公孫鞅，年雖少，有奇才，願王舉國而聽之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "」王嘿然。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "王且去，座屏人言曰：「王即不聽用鞅，必殺之，無令出境。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "」王許諾而去。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "公叔座召鞅謝曰：「今者王問可以為相者，我言若，王色不許我。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "我方先君後臣，因謂王即弗用鞅，當殺之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "王許我。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "汝可疾去矣，且見禽。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "」鞅曰：「彼王不能用君之言任臣，又安能用君之言殺臣乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "」卒不去。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "惠王既去，而謂左右曰：「公叔病甚，悲乎，欲令寡人以國聽公孫鞅也，豈不悖哉！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "公叔既死，公孫鞅聞秦孝公下令國中求賢者，將修繆公之業，東復侵地，乃遂西入秦，因孝公寵臣景監以求見孝公。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "孝公既見衛鞅，語事良久，孝公時時睡，弗聽。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "罷而孝公怒景監曰：「子之客妄人耳，安足用邪！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "」景監以讓衛鞅。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "衛鞅曰：「吾說公以帝道，其志不開悟矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "」後五日，復求見鞅。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "鞅復見孝公，益愈，然而未中旨。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "罷而孝公復讓景監，景監亦讓鞅。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "鞅曰：「吾說公以王道而未入也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "請復見鞅。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "」鞅復見孝公，孝公善之而未用也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "罷而去。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "孝公謂景監曰：「汝客善，可與語矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "」鞅曰：「吾說公以霸道，其意欲用之矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "誠復見我，我知之矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "」衛鞅復見孝公。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "公與語，不自知厀之前於席也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "語數日不厭。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "景監曰：「子何以中吾君？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "吾君之驩甚也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "」鞅曰：「吾說君以帝王之道比三代，而君曰：『久遠，吾不能待。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "且賢君者，各及其身顯名天下，安能邑邑待數十百年以成帝王乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "』故吾以彊國之術說君，君大說之耳。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0040",
          "zh": "然亦難以比德於殷周矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0041",
          "zh": "」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0042",
          "zh": "孝公既用衛鞅，鞅欲變法，恐天下議己。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0043",
          "zh": "衛鞅曰：「疑行無名，疑事無功。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0044",
          "zh": "且夫有高人之行者，固見非於世；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0045",
          "zh": "有獨知之慮者，必見敖於民。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0046",
          "zh": "愚者闇於成事，知者見於未萌。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0047",
          "zh": "民不可與慮始而可與樂成。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0048",
          "zh": "論至德者不和於俗，成大功者不謀於眾。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0049",
          "zh": "是以聖人茍可以彊國，不法其故；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0050",
          "zh": "茍可以利民，不循其禮。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0051",
          "zh": "」孝公曰：「善。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0052",
          "zh": "」甘龍曰：「不然。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0053",
          "zh": "聖人不易民而教，知者不變法而治。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0054",
          "zh": "因民而教，不勞而成功；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0055",
          "zh": "緣法而治者，吏習而民安之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0056",
          "zh": "」衛鞅曰：「龍之所言，世俗之言也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0057",
          "zh": "常人安於故俗，學者溺於所聞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0058",
          "zh": "以此兩者居官守法可也，非所與論於法之外也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0059",
          "zh": "三代不同禮而王，五伯不同法而霸。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0060",
          "zh": "智者作法，愚者制焉；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0061",
          "zh": "賢者更禮，不肖者拘焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0062",
          "zh": "」杜摯曰：「利不百，不變法；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0063",
          "zh": "功不十，不易器。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0064",
          "zh": "法古無過，循禮無邪。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0065",
          "zh": "」衛鞅曰：「治世不一道，便國不法古。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0066",
          "zh": "故湯武不循古而王，夏殷不易禮而亡。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0067",
          "zh": "反古者不可非，而循禮者不足多。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0068",
          "zh": "」孝公曰：「善。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0069",
          "zh": "」以衛鞅為左庶長，卒定變法之令。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0070",
          "zh": "令民為什伍，而相牧司連坐。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0071",
          "zh": "不告姦者腰斬，告姦者與斬敵首同賞，匿姦者與降敵同罰。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0072",
          "zh": "民有二男以上不分異者，倍其賦。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0073",
          "zh": "有軍功者，各以率受上爵；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0074",
          "zh": "為私斗者，各以輕重被刑大小。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0075",
          "zh": "僇力本業，耕織致粟帛多者復其身。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0076",
          "zh": "事末利及怠而貧者，舉以為收孥。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0077",
          "zh": "宗室非有軍功論，不得為屬籍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0078",
          "zh": "明尊卑爵秩等級，各以差次名田宅，臣妾衣服以家次。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0079",
          "zh": "有功者顯榮，無功者雖富無所芬華。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0080",
          "zh": "令既具，未布，恐民之不信，已乃立三丈之木於國都市南門，募民有能徙置北門者予十金。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0081",
          "zh": "民怪之，莫敢徙。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0082",
          "zh": "復曰「能徙者予五十金」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0083",
          "zh": "有一人徙之，輒予五十金，以明不欺。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0084",
          "zh": "卒下令。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0085",
          "zh": "令行於民朞年，秦民之國都言初令之不便者以千數。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0086",
          "zh": "於是太子犯法。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0087",
          "zh": "衛鞅曰：「法之不行，自上犯之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0088",
          "zh": "」將法太子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0089",
          "zh": "太子，君嗣也，不可施刑，刑其傅公子虔，黥其師公孫賈。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0090",
          "zh": "明日，秦人皆趨令。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0091",
          "zh": "行之十年，秦民大說，道不拾遺，山無盜賊，家給人足。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0092",
          "zh": "民勇於公戰，怯於私斗，鄉邑大治。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0093",
          "zh": "秦民初言令不便者有來言令便者，衛鞅曰「此皆亂化之民也」，盡遷之於邊城。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0094",
          "zh": "其後民莫敢議令。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0095",
          "zh": "於是以鞅為大良造。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0096",
          "zh": "將兵圍魏安邑，降之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0097",
          "zh": "居三年，作為筑冀闕宮庭於咸陽，秦自雍徙都之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0098",
          "zh": "而令民父子兄弟同室內息者為禁。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0099",
          "zh": "而集小（都）鄉邑聚為縣，置令、丞，凡三十一縣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0100",
          "zh": "為田開阡陌封疆，而賦稅平。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0101",
          "zh": "平斗桶權衡丈尺。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0102",
          "zh": "行之四年，公子虔復犯約，劓之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0103",
          "zh": "居五年，秦人富彊，天子致胙於孝公，諸侯畢賀。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0104",
          "zh": "其明年，齊敗魏兵於馬陵，虜其太子申，殺將軍龐涓。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0105",
          "zh": "其明年，衛鞅說孝公曰：「秦之與魏，譬若人之有腹心疾，非魏并秦，秦即并魏。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0106",
          "zh": "何者？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0107",
          "zh": "魏居領阨之西，都安邑，與秦界河而獨擅山東之利。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0108",
          "zh": "利則西侵秦，病則東收地。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0109",
          "zh": "今以君之賢聖，國賴以盛。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0110",
          "zh": "而魏往年大破於齊，諸侯畔之，可因此時伐魏。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0111",
          "zh": "魏不支秦，必東徙。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0112",
          "zh": "東徙，秦據河山之固，東鄉以制諸侯，此帝王之業也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0113",
          "zh": "」孝公以為然，使衛鞅將而伐魏。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0114",
          "zh": "魏使公子卬將而擊之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0115",
          "zh": "軍既相距，衛鞅遺魏將公子卬書曰：「吾始與公子驩，今俱為兩國將，不忍相攻，可與公子面相見，盟，樂飲而罷兵，以安秦魏。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0116",
          "zh": "」魏公子卬以為然。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0117",
          "zh": "會盟已，飲，而衛鞅伏甲士而襲虜魏公子卬，因攻其軍，盡破之以歸秦。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0118",
          "zh": "魏惠王兵數破於齊秦，國內空，日以削，恐，乃使使割河西之地獻於秦以和。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0119",
          "zh": "而魏遂去安邑，徙都大梁。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0120",
          "zh": "梁惠王曰：「寡人恨不用公叔座之言也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0121",
          "zh": "」衛鞅既破魏還，秦封之於、商十五邑，號為商君。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0122",
          "zh": "商君相秦十年，宗室貴戚多怨望者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0123",
          "zh": "趙良見商君。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0124",
          "zh": "商君曰：「鞅之得見也，從孟蘭皋，今鞅請得交，可乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0125",
          "zh": "」趙良曰：「仆弗敢願也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0126",
          "zh": "孔丘有言曰：『推賢而戴者進，聚不肖而王者退。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0127",
          "zh": "』仆不肖，故不敢受命。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0128",
          "zh": "仆聞之曰：『非其位而居之曰貪位，非其名而有之曰貪名。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0129",
          "zh": "』仆聽君之義，則恐仆貪位貪名也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0130",
          "zh": "故不敢聞命。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0131",
          "zh": "」商君曰：「子不說吾治秦與？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0132",
          "zh": "」趙良曰：「反聽之謂聰，內視之謂明，自勝之謂彊。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0133",
          "zh": "虞舜有言曰：『自卑也尚矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0134",
          "zh": "』君不若道虞舜之道，無為問仆矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0135",
          "zh": "」商君曰：「始秦戎翟之教，父子無別，同室而居。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0136",
          "zh": "今我更制其教，而為其男女之別，大筑冀闕，營如魯衛矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0137",
          "zh": "子觀我治秦也，孰與五羖大夫賢？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0138",
          "zh": "」趙良曰：「千羊之皮，不如一狐之掖；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0139",
          "zh": "千人之諾諾，不如一士之諤諤。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0140",
          "zh": "武王諤諤以昌，殷紂墨墨以亡。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0141",
          "zh": "君若不非武王乎，則仆請終日正言而無誅，可乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0142",
          "zh": "」商君曰：「語有之矣，貌言華也，至言實也，苦言藥也，甘言疾也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0143",
          "zh": "夫子果肯終日正言，鞅之藥也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0144",
          "zh": "鞅將事子，子又何辭焉！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0145",
          "zh": "」趙良曰：「夫五羖大夫，荊之鄙人也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0146",
          "zh": "聞秦繆公之賢而願望見，行而無資，自粥於秦客，被褐食牛。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0147",
          "zh": "期年，繆公知之，舉之牛口之下，而加之百姓之上，秦國莫敢望焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0148",
          "zh": "相秦六七年，而東伐鄭，三置晉國之君，一救荊國之禍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0149",
          "zh": "發教封內，而巴人致貢；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0150",
          "zh": "施德諸侯，而八戎來服。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0151",
          "zh": "由余聞之，款關請見。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0152",
          "zh": "五羖大夫之相秦也，勞不坐乘，暑不張蓋，行於國中，不從車乘，不操干戈，功名藏於府庫，德行施於後世。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0153",
          "zh": "五羖大夫死，秦國男女流涕，童子不歌謠，舂者不相杵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0154",
          "zh": "此五羖大夫之德也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0155",
          "zh": "今君之見秦王也，因嬖人景監以為主，非所以為名也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0156",
          "zh": "相秦不以百姓為事，而大筑冀闕，非所以為功也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0157",
          "zh": "刑黥太子之師傅，殘傷民以駿刑，是積怨畜禍也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0158",
          "zh": "教之化民也深於命，民之效上也捷於令。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0159",
          "zh": "今君又左建外易，非所以為教也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0160",
          "zh": "君又南面而稱寡人，日繩秦之貴公子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0161",
          "zh": "《詩》曰：『相鼠有體，人而無禮，人而無禮，何不遄死。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0162",
          "zh": "』以詩觀之，非所以為壽也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0163",
          "zh": "公子虔杜門不出已八年矣，君又殺祝懽而黥公孫賈。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0164",
          "zh": "《詩》曰：『得人者興，失人者崩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0165",
          "zh": "』此數事者，非所以得人也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0166",
          "zh": "君之出也，後車十數，從車載甲，多力而駢脅者為驂乘，持矛而操闟戟者旁車而趨。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0167",
          "zh": "此一物不具，君固不出。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0168",
          "zh": "《書》曰：『恃德者昌，恃力者亡。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0169",
          "zh": "』君之危若朝露，尚將欲延年益壽乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0170",
          "zh": "則何不歸十五都，灌園於鄙，勸秦王顯巖穴之士，養老存孤，敬父兄，序有功，尊有德，可以少安。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0171",
          "zh": "君尚將貪商於之富，寵秦國之教，畜百姓之怨，秦王一旦捐賓客而不立朝，秦國之所以收君者，豈其微哉？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0172",
          "zh": "亡可翹足而待。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0173",
          "zh": "」商君弗從。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0174",
          "zh": "後五月而秦孝公卒，太子立。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0175",
          "zh": "公子虔之徒告商君欲反，發吏捕商君。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0176",
          "zh": "商君亡至關下，欲舍客舍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0177",
          "zh": "客人不知其是商君也，曰：「商君之法，舍人無驗者坐之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0178",
          "zh": "」商君喟然嘆曰：「嗟乎，為法之敝一至此哉！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0179",
          "zh": "」去之魏。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0180",
          "zh": "魏人怨其欺公子卬而破魏師，弗受。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0181",
          "zh": "商君欲之他國。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0182",
          "zh": "魏人曰：「商君，秦之賊。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0183",
          "zh": "秦彊而賊入魏，弗歸，不可。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0184",
          "zh": "」遂內秦。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0185",
          "zh": "商君既復入秦，走商邑，與其徒屬發邑兵北出擊鄭。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0186",
          "zh": "秦發兵攻商君，殺之於鄭黽池。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0187",
          "zh": "秦惠王車裂商君以徇，曰：「莫如商鞅反者！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0188",
          "zh": "」遂滅商君之家。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0189",
          "zh": "太史公曰：商君，其天資刻薄人也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "Source: Chinese Text Project http://ctext.org/shiji Partial translation adapted from Herbert J.",
              "translator": "Herbert J. Allen (1894)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0190",
          "zh": "跡其欲干孝公以帝王術，挾持浮說，非其質矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "Allen's \"Ssŭma Ch'ien's Historical Records\" (Royal Asiatic Society,",
              "translator": "Herbert J. Allen (1894)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0191",
          "zh": "且所因由嬖臣，及得用，刑公子虔，欺魏將卬，不師趙良之言，亦足發明商君之少恩矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "1894).",
              "translator": "Herbert J. Allen (1894)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0192",
          "zh": "余嘗讀商君開塞耕戰書，與其人行事相類。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "Dictionary cache status: not loaded Glossary and Other Vocabulary",
              "translator": "Herbert J. Allen (1894)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0193",
          "zh": "卒受惡名於秦，有以也夫！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Source: Chinese Text Project http://ctext.org/shiji Partial translation adapted from Herbert J. Allen's \"Ssŭma Ch'ien's Historical Records\" (Royal Asiatic Society, 1894). Dictionary cache status: not loaded Glossary and Other Vocabulary",
          "translator": "Herbert J. Allen (1894)"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
